Some adjectives that my friends and family use to describe me: Independent-minded, Loyal, Passionate, Prudent, Witty, Efficient, Goal-oriented, Honest, Intelligent and Sharp. I can be strong yet emotional, lazy in leisure and hard-working at work. I can cook a decent meal or two, and know how to run a house. But ask me to stay at home, and I am going to come down with cabin fever. It takes time to gain my confidence, but once it is done, you will find that I am a very caring and understanding person, and a loyal supporter in your life-goals. I have spent a major part of my life in Delhi, and speak good Hindi. I speak with my family in Telugu and use Hindi and English at work and with my Delhi friends. I love Punjabi food and Punjabi music, apart from South-Indian cuisine and Telugu movies. In fact, I love spicy food and any cuisine that is spicy would get my vote. Music makes me happy and I like to sing, although I can't say I get the tunes right. For the right partner, I am willing to relocate to any city, whichever country it is in. about1: I am working as a Behavioural Skills and Language Trainer. Setting up a Telugu Training Institute and training Government officials on job orientation are my professional goals. I love children. Working for the betterment of juvenile homes, social welfare hostels and children on the whole is my personal goal. I love arts and crafts. Making flowers, greeting cards, painting are my favourites. I cannot live without reading books. I love people. I will know the people who meet me in my life, and then love them with their good and bad qualities. But I keep facing issues for being very friendly. I love joint family. Whats a family without elders and children. Being with me is very easy, yet very tough. Its because I do not demand materialistic things. Whatever I expect from my life partner is love, compassion, courage, responsibility and the willingness to be a good human being everyday. I have zero tolerance to male ego or feminism. I can live with human beings, not "MAN" or "WOMAN". Cooking is my passion. I cannot take even small traits of cruelty, negligence, cheating, irresponsibility. For me love needs to be expressed. Trust and respect build relationships for me. Just true love from my life partner, and I can make life heaven.
about2: I am looking for a partner who can understand my nature. I'm cannot be a typical house wife staying at home. I'm also not a career woman. I earn money so that I have it for smooth running of life. Money and looks are not a matter for me which change with times. Character is something that I cannot compromise on. Especially, after marriage, I cannot tolerate if the person is not honest to me. I'm very affectionate, caring. I can make anyone's life heaven. Laziness, cowardliness, opportunism, negligence, sarcasm, dishonesty are some traits that I cannot bear. He should love his parents and family. Should have respect towards elders and everyone. People lacking energy to organize their lives cannot just do anything. Universal and unconditional love are very important. Its not enough for me if my partner just loves me and doesn't care for others. I do care for him and everyone, and expect the same. Above all, its not just my partner who's important, its all the family that's important. Even if one person is not comfortable, the whole family gets disturbed. I am into social activism. Though I'm into training profile right now, after 10 years, I would get into my profession, as an advocate and activist, dealing with human rights, women, child rights and environment cases. They are highly challenging and sometimes very risky. Anyone who has the courage to face any kind of situations in life only can do these. So even the family I'm married into should have these traits to accept. For instance, sometimes, I might get a child victim home and might have to protect for months, then right now I have no issues, but even later, I shouldn't have. I might be anything outside, but at home I'm completely into my family is cooking, cleaning, organizing, celebrating, taking care of the family members, kids, guests, grand parents, everyone and everything. I give my 100% to my family. All I expect is sincere love just towards me as a partner - unconditional, true.
about_family: I live with my parents. Grandmother(maternal) lives with us. Sister and brother-in-law live in next street. We all live together.
